NOTICE — Third-Party Components & Attributions
===============================================

This project builds upon the following open-source works. All rights belong
to their respective authors. Please comply with each component's license terms
when using or distributing this software.

1. BetterBox-TTS (TTS Core — Vietnamese)
   Author  : Dolly VN / ContextBoxAI
   Source  : https://github.com/nowtranminh1-TTS/BetterBox-TTS
   License : Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 (CC BY-NC 4.0)
   Usage   : Vietnamese Text-to-Speech synthesis engine (Trạm 3 — offline TTS)
   Note    : This component PROHIBITS commercial use. The entire project
             inherits this restriction.

2. GIPFormer (ASR & Denoising — Vietnamese)
   Author  : G-Group AI Lab
   Source  : https://huggingface.co/g-group-ai-lab/gipformer-65M-rnnt
   License : MIT License
   Usage   : Efficient Vietnamese speech recognition & noise-robust audio
             pre-processing (Trạm 0 — Denoise, Trạm 1 — ASR)

3. SenseVoice Small (ASR & Emotion Extraction)
   Author  : FunAudioLLM / Alibaba
   Source  : https://github.com/FunAudioLLM/SenseVoice
   License : MIT License
   Usage   : Multilingual speech recognition and emotion extraction (Trạm 1 — ASR)

4. envit5-translation (Machine Translation)
   Author  : VietAI
   Source  : https://huggingface.co/VietAI/envit5-translation
   License : MIT License
   Usage   : Bilingual translation engine (Trạm 2 — VI↔EN)

5. F5-TTS (Voice Cloning)
   Author  : SWivid
   Source  : https://github.com/SWivid/F5-TTS
   License : MIT License
   Usage   : Zero-shot voice cloning and speech synthesis (Trạm 3 — TTS)

6. Silero VAD (Voice Activity Detection)
   Author  : Silero Team
   Source  : https://github.com/snakers4/silero-vad
   License : MIT License
   Usage   : Real-time voice activity detection to trigger pipeline processing.
